      </section>

      <!-- Spread Betting Section -->
      <section class="spread-betting-section">
        <h2>Tax-Free Spread Betting for UK Traders</h2>
        <div class="spread-betting-content">
          <div class="spread-betting-text">
            <p>
              <strong>Spread betting</strong> is a unique trading method available to United Kingdom and Ireland residents that offers
              significant tax advantages. Unlike traditional CFD trading, spread betting profits are currently exempt from
              both Capital Gains Tax and Stamp Duty in the UK.
